      "width": 415,
      "height": 49,
      "text": "Four people P, Q, R, S live on floors 1 to 4 (one on each\nfloor). P is not on the 1st or 4th floor. Q lives above P.\nS lives on the 1st floor. Who lives on which floor?",
      "fontSize": 13,
