      "groupIds": [
        "type_3"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Five students P, Q, R, S, T have different heights. P is\ntaller than Q, T is taller than R who is taller than S,\nand Q is taller than T. Arrange them from tallest to\nshortest.",
