    {
      "id": "el_38",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 65,
      "y": 1336,
      "width": 303,
      "height": 216,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: B>A>C and C>E>F -> B>A>C>E>F\nStep 2: D is tallest -> D first\nStep 3: Full: D>B>A>C>E>F\n\n  D──→B──→A──→C──→E──→F\n  1st 2nd 3rd 4th 5th 6th\n      (tallest → shortest)\n\nTRICK:\nPlace the absolute clue first (D=tallest).\nMerge chains via common element (C).\n3rd position = A.\n\nAnswer: 3rd tallest = A ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 3800,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 38,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "groupIds": [
        "type_4"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: B>A>C and C>E>F -> B>A>C>E>F\nStep 2: D is tallest -> D first\nStep 3: Full: D>B>A>C>E>F\n\n  D──→B──→A──→C──→E──→F\n  1st 2nd 3rd 4th 5th 6th\n      (tallest → shortest)\n\nTRICK:\nPlace the absolute clue first (D=tallest).\nMerge chains via common element (C).\n3rd position = A.\n\nAnswer: 3rd tallest = A ✓",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
