      "text": "Three people A, B, C each own one pet (cat, dog, fish) and\ndrink one beverage (tea, coffee, milk). A does not own the\ncat. The coffee drinker owns the dog. B drinks tea. Who\nowns the fish?",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 13,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
