      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Three people A, B, C each own one pet (cat, dog, fish) and\ndrink one beverage (tea, coffee, milk). A does not own the\ncat. The coffee drinker owns the dog. B drinks tea. Who\nowns the fish?",
