    {
      "id": "el_68",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 65,
      "y": 2238,
      "width": 303,
      "height": 188,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: Input: 45 13 67 29 8 51\nStep 2: Each step picks smallest unsorted\n  I:  [8] 45 13 67 29 51\n  II: 8 [13] 45 67 29 51\n  III:8 13 [29] 45 67 51\n  IV: 8 13 29 [45] 51 67\n\nTRICK:\nPattern = selection sort (pick next min).\nCount steps = count unsorted elements - 1.\n\nAnswer: Step IV = 8 13 29 45 51 67 ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
