      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: Input: 45 13 67 29 8 51\nStep 2: Each step picks smallest unsorted\n  I:  [8] 45 13 67 29 51\n  II: 8 [13] 45 67 29 51\n  III:8 13 [29] 45 67 51\n  IV: 8 13 29 [45] 51 67\n\nTRICK:\nPattern = selection sort (pick next min).\nCount steps = count unsorted elements - 1.\n\nAnswer: Step IV = 8 13 29 45 51 67 ✓",
      "autoResize": true,
